  <abstract id="abstr_chi" date-changed="20091228" lang="chi" format="original">
    <p num="1">本发明属于化工技术领域，具体涉及一种B阶段环氧树脂溶液及其制备方法。采用酯环族环氧树脂——二氧化双环戊二烯为原料树脂，马来酸酐为固化剂，三羟甲基丙烷为催化剂，以二甲苯为溶剂，通过溶液聚合工艺合成了B阶段的环氧树脂溶液，合成反应时间大为缩短，产物可以用作浸渍料、胶粘剂和自粘结漆与涂料等。</p>
  </abstract>
  <abstract id="abstr_eng" date-changed="20091228" lang="eng" format="original">
    <p>The patent refers to the field of 'macromolecular compounds obtained otherwise than by reactions only involving carbon-to-carbon unsaturated bonds'. A B-stage epoxy resin solution and its preparation are disclosed. The process is carried out by taking bicylclic pentadiene as raw material resin, taking maleic anhydride as curing agent, taking tri-hydroxymethyl propane as catalyst, taking dimethyl benzene as solvent, polymerizing and synthesizing to obtain final product. It shortens synthetic time and can be used as impregnating material, binder and self-adhesive pigment and coating.</p>
  </abstract>
